{"type": "article", "id": 28379, "title": "卖茶，可以有几种姿势？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-06-18T07:03:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 5134, "name": "茶叶"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 874, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703150915trGPTcSHW84Nh5xO.jpg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\r\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>印象中茶的受欢迎程度并不低于咖啡，但适合年轻人的茶叶品牌或“茶馆”却很难找到，城市里的街道早已被大大小小的咖啡馆占据了。英国一家茶饮品牌 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26749.html\">Good &amp; Proper </a>创始人从一辆流动车开始推广茶，在悉尼，“<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19688.html\">兔子洞有机茶吧</a>”（the Rabbit Hole Organic Tea Bar）立志于营造更轻松随性的气氛。</p>\r\n<p>为了吸引年轻的消费者，越来越多的茶叶品牌在强调茶叶的特质和健康属性之外，对颜值也是越来越讲究。本周我们挑选了几个茶叶包装以及零售店的设计，他们大多打破了我们对于茶叶的刻板印象，给人一种更亲和、时尚的感觉。</p>\r\n<h2>H Tea by minimalist</h2>\r\n<p>韩国首尔有这么一家看上去很冷淡的茶叶店 H Tea，<a href=\"http://minimalist.kr/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalist</a> 在设计时以蒂凡尼蓝和黑白作为主色调，呈现出一种酷酷的现代感。H Tea 的茶叶被储存在圆柱形的铁罐里，设计师们设计了一套次级调色板以区分不同种类的茶叶。茶罐整齐划一地摆放在白色的货架上，既是展示又起到了装饰的效果，让人眼前一亮。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150858THurkQvS1pgq8Rys.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150858QzHNVlxwn8dFXItE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150859K4hV9AkblZCp6yqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150900nt8iFOIVS5eQKwpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150900ZTA4Hi12UG9n7M0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Saudade Tea by canaria inc.</h2>\r\n<p>日本的茶叶品牌 Saudade 采用了水彩画作为外包装，<a href=\"http://www.canaria-world.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">canaria inc.</a> 特意设计了两套不同的风格。一种是讲述了茶叶故事的插画，明快的颜色描绘出了一幅幅清新自然的田园景象，带领人们进行一次“茶叶之旅”，强调了茶叶的“有机”概念。另一种风格则使用了各种不规则图案，同样透露着淡雅的和式风情。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150901TVYg835iw6CbanWB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53323486\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150901PK0fU1m7hngauw5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150902jgFptqrMK9femnR0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031509034MWEhJ7mFKGbQtlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150903qkhBQzEK94vVDp7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150903nhgtaRBrDSKX7ZiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Good Moment by Serlick et al.</h2>\r\n<p>台湾的“食辰”是一款不太一样的茶叶，对应器官的运作时间，有针对性地调配出了 12 款中药茶饮。每一种茶叶都被装在金字塔形的小纸盒中，由上而下可以看到别致的设计字体。纸盒分为日夜两组，一侧标注了时间和单品名称，另一侧则烫上金银两色的局部图案，把一组拼在一起时就会显示出一朵完整的花。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150904ahYKOspRSN3b8jyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65531915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150904TS0Phmd4fIOQeYJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150905VYkgaUCJEx6wt9sT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150905IPD0FzXQ6eGg4dEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150906kG7tSwszqdc5efLV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>The Gourmet Tea by Alan Chu</h2>\r\n<p>这家在巴西的茶吧外表看上去像是由方形色块拼出来的墙，卖茶的窗台和储藏茶具的柜子全都藏在其中。白天，依靠柜子下面的滑轮可将这些柜子全都拉出来，到了晚上打烊时，这里又恢复成了一面彩色的墙，就像是一个代表着欢乐和活力的城市雕塑。这种灵活改变的方式也使这里拥有街头小吃的特征，更能融入周围的环境。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150906r0sniFPokTX7dhux.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10470085\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150907SkQrVsv8PWon43fI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031509072BtXoCWNjfdqRU3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150908A4hYJCnUWSikdVRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031509089SmJjgNy32a7VTo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Tombo Tea by Natsko Seki</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://tombotea.myshopify.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tombo </a>是一家在英国的日料餐厅，他们专门引入了抹茶并邀请日本插画师 Natsko Seki 设计平面。Natsko Seki 曾为 LV 等时尚品牌设计，在这组茶包装中，同样使用了一种有城市文化风格的图像。穿着日本和服的人们走在樱花树下，或者跪坐着喝茶，而在人头处又是真实的照片，让这些跳出传统的认识进入更现代的视角。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150909th7uG9zlIFRHKAOp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150909TSzv2Z1eKVcoPOXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031509105fHqIVWDPd8BNCja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150910Udun59iNwDagr3Z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150910Ytjyix0JXsBcH7ZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150911D9OIolivf1Bt6USq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Paper &amp; Tea by Fabian von Ferrari </h2>\r\n<p>柏林的茶叶品牌 <a href=\"http://www.paperandtea.com/de/?redirect\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paper &amp; Tea</a> 为人称道的是店铺体验，它将自己的店做成一种博物馆。不同茶装在了玻璃器皿中，配上大量的说明文字和用法变成一种固定的样本，鼓励人们走进触摸品尝。在这些样本中间还展示了完整的茶具，让人们可以对喝茶有更多的认识和亲近。他们的包装喜欢用纯白色的盒子，非常素雅干净。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150911PaUrL9XEN0BmHDSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150912GFfAqKLdYkpEP2MR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150913dDvFkOjZtg8mzrxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150913SnkvWzysQ35VP9cg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150914jY5dNLIkuvTXhBFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61806311\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150914TPYrKAyRVgaveb3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150915MIKw2PHkXpCaT19z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n"}